	section#features_main.col-md-7.get-certified
		.row
			.col-sm-12
				h2 How To Get Certified
		.certified.text-left
			.row.colored-icon
				.col-sm-12.gray
					.row
						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>1</sup> <a href="http://app.webriq.com/sites/create" target="_blank">Create an account</a>
						.col-sm-12.details
							p Create your free account and start creating your own static website.
							p
								img(src="img/register.jpg").img-responsive

				.col-sm-12.red
					.row

						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>2</sup> Use WebriQ Boilerplate
						.col-sm-12.details

							p Navigate to <strong>Quicklinks</strong> Developer <i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> Boilerplate or you can go directly to <a href="http://boilerplate.webriq.com/" target="_blank"><strong>boilerplate.webriq.com</strong></a>. Use the documentation to start building your site
							p
								img(src="img/boiler.jpg").img-responsive

				.col-sm-12.teal
					.row
						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>3</sup> Create Slack Account On WebriQHQ
						.col-sm-12.details

							p Go to <a href="http://slackin.webriq.com/" target="_blanck"><strong>slackin.webriq.com</strong></a>  to create your account and start chatting with other developers or chat with one of WebriQ developers on the <strong>Q&A</strong> channel
							p
								img(src="img/createacctslack.jpg").img-responsive

				.col-sm-12.navy
					.row
						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>4</sup> Submit Domain
						.col-sm-12.details
							p Once you are done submit your domain(s) to <a href="mailto:getcertified@webriq.com"><strong>getcertified@webriq.com</strong></a>
							p
								img(src="img/submitdomain.jpg").img-responsive

				.col-sm-12.purple
					.row
						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>5</sup> Website Review
						.col-sm-12.details

							p Upon positive review you will receive a WebriQ Developers certificate and a <strong>70%</strong> discount on our <strong>PRO</strong> service for a period of 1 Year, representing a value of <strong>$245</strong> per year per site.
							p
								img(src="img/review.jpg").img-responsive

				.col-sm-12.yellow
					.row
						.col-sm-12.title
							h3<sup>6</sup> Profile Listed
						.col-sm-12.details

							p Your profile will be listed in our APP, so that potential customers on the platform can contact you for jobs that need to be done on websites on the WebriQ platform.
